#{100}{}{You see Canary.}
{100}{}{你看到金丝雀了。 -- You see Canary.}
#{101}{}{You see a completely ordinary bum... Or so he appears.}
{101}{}{你看到一个完全普通的流浪汉。。。他似乎是这样的。 -- You see a completely ordinary bum... Or so he appears.}
#{102}{}{Er, hello.}
{102}{}{呃，你好。 -- Er, hello.}
#{109}{}{Oh, and what could a poor old hobo like myself do for you, sir?}
{109}{}{噢，像我这样可怜的流浪汉能为你做些什么，先生？ -- Oh, and what could a poor old hobo like myself do for you, sir?}
#{110}{}{Oh, gracious sir, could you spare just a bit to help a poor old hobo down on his luck?}
{110}{}{噢，仁慈的先生，你能抽出一点时间来帮助一个可怜的流浪汉吗？ -- Oh, gracious sir, could you spare just a bit to help a poor old hobo down on his luck?}
#{111}{}{Who are you?}
{111}{}{你是谁？ -- Who are you?}
#{112}{}{Of course, here's 10 bucks for food.}
{112}{}{当然，这是10块钱买食物。 -- Of course, here's 10 bucks for food.}
#{113}{}{I have a question.}
{113}{}{我有个问题。 -- I have a question.}
#{114}{}{Not today.}
{114}{}{今天不行。 -- Not today.}
#{115}{}{I only have one thing to say: "The gilding is gone from our century."}
{115}{}{我只有一句话要说：“镀金已经从我们的世纪消失了。” -- I only have one thing to say: "The gilding is gone from our century."}
#{116}{}{The name's Canary, sir. Just a small, wandering hobo in a large world.}
{116}{}{我叫金丝雀，先生。只是大世界里一个小小的流浪汉。 -- The name's Canary, sir. Just a small, wandering hobo in a large world.}
#{117}{}{Hello, Canary. And goodbye.}
{117}{}{你好，金丝雀。再见。 -- Hello, Canary. And goodbye.}
#{118}{}{It came down into our pockets, amigo.}
{118}{}{它掉进了我们的口袋，朋友。 -- It came down into our pockets, amigo.}
#{119}{}{Is that all you have to say?}
{119}{}{你就想说这些吗？ -- Is that all you have to say?}
#{120}{}{I'm just a simple hobo. What more could you want from me? I've already said more than my mind can handle.}
{120}{}{我只是个普通的流浪汉。你还想从我这里得到什么？我已经说得太多了。 -- I'm just a simple hobo. What more could you want from me? I've already said more than my mind can handle.}
#{121}{}{If you say so...}
{121}{}{如果你这样说。。。 -- If you say so...}
#{122}{}{Err... [as you turn to leave, he taps his pocket and looks at you expectantly]}
{122}{}{呃。。。[当你转身离开时，他轻拍口袋，期待地看着你] -- Err... [as you turn to leave, he taps his pocket and looks at you expectantly]}
#{123}{}{Sure, here's 10 bucks, philosopher.}
{123}{}{当然，这是10美元，哲学家。 -- Sure, here's 10 bucks, philosopher.}
#{124}{}{Sorry, I'm all out.}
{124}{}{对不起，我没空了。 -- Sorry, I'm all out.}
#{125}{}{Piss off, you're not getting anything from me!}
{125}{}{滚开，你从我这里什么都得不到！ -- Piss off, you're not getting anything from me!}
#{126}{}{[He scowls and angrily adjusts his rags] Get away from my fire! This is my spot!}
{126}{}{[他怒目而视，怒气冲冲地整理衣服]离我的火远点！这是我的地盘！ -- [He scowls and angrily adjusts his rags] Get away from my fire! This is my spot!}
#{127}{}{Fine, here's 10 bucks.}
{127}{}{好吧，这是10美元。 -- Fine, here's 10 bucks.}
#{128}{}{Ha! There's no arguing with that, is there?}
{128}{}{哈！这是无可争辩的，是吗？ -- Ha! There's no arguing with that, is there?}
#{129}{}{Thank you, sir!}
{129}{}{谢谢，先生！ -- Thank you, sir!}
#{130}{}{You're welcome.}
{130}{}{不客气。 -- You're welcome.}
#{131}{}{Now, can you answer a few questions?}
{131}{}{现在，你能回答几个问题吗？ -- Now, can you answer a few questions?}
#{132}{}{I would, I would, but ohh... The hunger, it makes it hard to think...}
{132}{}{我会的，我会的，但是哦。。。饥饿，让人难以思考。。。 -- I would, I would, but ohh... The hunger, it makes it hard to think...}
#{133}{}{Here's 10 bucks to sate those hunger pangs.}
{133}{}{这是10块钱来充饥。 -- Here's 10 bucks to sate those hunger pangs.}
#{134}{}{Wait up, I'll be back.}
{134}{}{等等，我会回来的。 -- Wait up, I'll be back.}
#{135}{}{Of course, sir, happy to help.}
{135}{}{当然，先生，很乐意帮忙。 -- Of course, sir, happy to help.}
#{136}{}{What do you know about this place?}
{136}{}{你对这个地方了解多少？ -- What do you know about this place?}
#{137}{}{What's behind that fence?}
{137}{}{栅栏后面是什么？ -- What's behind that fence?}
#{138}{}{Have you ever seen the owner of this ranch?}
{138}{}{你见过这个牧场的主人吗？ -- Have you ever seen the owner of this ranch?}
#{139}{}{How did you end up like this?}
{139}{}{你怎么会变成这样？ -- How did you end up like this?}
#{140}{}{I've heard enough.}
{140}{}{我听够了。 -- I've heard enough.}
#{141}{}{[He draws a big circle with his hands] A ranch! It's enormous! They make food here - the most important thing in this world.}
{141}{}{[他用手画了一个大圆圈]一个牧场！太大了！他们在这里制造食物――这是世界上最重要的东西。 -- [He draws a big circle with his hands] A ranch! It's enormous! They make food here - the most important thing in this world.}
#{142}{}{This is the home of a great man. He owns this ranch and lives here with his family, guards, slaves, and brahmin. Oh, he guards it carefully... Step inside, and they'll shoot you on sight, unless you're one of their own!}
{142}{}{这是一个伟人的家。他拥有这个牧场，和他的家人、守卫、奴隶和婆罗门住在这里。哦，他小心地保护着它。。。进去，他们一看到你就会开枪，除非你是他们自己人！ -- This is the home of a great man. He owns this ranch and lives here with his family, guards, slaves, and brahmin. Oh, he guards it carefully... Step inside, and they'll shoot you on sight, unless you're one of their own!}
#{143}{}{Ohh, there's not many like him in Reno. A tough nut, for sure - but do you know how nuts spoil? Not from the outside, no, but from within!}
{143}{}{哦，里诺没有多少像他这样的人。当然是个硬汉，但你知道坚果是怎么变质的吗？不是从外面，不是，而是从里面！ -- Ohh, there's not many like him in Reno. A tough nut, for sure - but do you know how nuts spoil? Not from the outside, no, but from within!}
#{144}{}{Me? Oh, wanderer, what could interest you in an old hobo like me? I was born from dust, I live by dust, and one day soon I will return to dust. They'll forget me then, but not yet - sometimes the guards come by and ask me to bring something into or out of the city. Easier than sending a slave or a guard, yes?}
{144}{}{我？哦，流浪汉，你对我这样的老流浪汉有什么兴趣？我生在尘土中，活在尘土中，总有一天我会回到尘土中。那时他们会忘记我，但现在还不会――有时卫兵会过来让我带些东西进城或出城。比派一个奴隶或守卫容易，是吗？ -- Me? Oh, wanderer, what could interest you in an old hobo like me? I was born from dust, I live by dust, and one day soon I will return to dust. They'll forget me then, but not yet - sometimes the guards come by and ask me to bring something into or out of the city. Easier than sending a slave or a guard, yes?}
#{145}{}{I see. Let me ask you something else.}
{145}{}{我懂了。我再问你一件事。 -- I see. Let me ask you something else.}
#{146}{}{No more questions for now.}
{146}{}{现在没有问题了。 -- No more questions for now.}
